. By designation of 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE94B0EFFAB4076B90D39A61357FDBF" pageId="12" pageNumber="79" refId="ref26885" refString="Steyskal, G. C. &amp; Verbeke, J. (1956) Sepedoninae (Sciomyzidae, Diptera) from Africa and southern Arabia. Bulletin de l'Institut royal des Sciences naturelles de Belgique, 32 (7), 1 - 14." type="journal article">Steyskal &amp; Verbeke (1956)</bibRefCitation>
.
